In a comment on the pull request, include the following information and check off the list.

 - [ ] Mini bio
  - Soft capped to 75 words
 - [ ] Desired date of publishing
  - Make sure this matches the `date` in the front matter
 - [ ] Social media contact info
 - [ ] Redaction: (yes|no)
  - Allow redaction, editing or structure changes by technical writer staff
 - [ ] Comments: (yes|no)
  - If you're willing to answer comments about your post, set `comments: true`.
  - Make sure to subscribe to your post comments by clicking on the **Subscribe** link at the very bottom of the post _once_ it's published.

